f_r(x) = \sum_{n=0}^{\lfloor \frac{r-1}{2} \rfloor}c_{r,n} x^{r-2n-1} = \sum_{n=0}^{\lfloor \frac{r-1}{2} \rfloor} \frac{ (2 r - 2 n)!!}{(r- 2n-1)!} x^{r-2n-1} 
X_{pq} = \int_{-1}^2 f_p(x) f_q(x) \mathrm{d} x = \sum_{n=0}^{\lfloor \frac{p-1}{2} \rfloor} \sum_{m=0}^{\lfloor \frac{q-1}{2} \rfloor} c_{p,n} c_{q,m} \int_{-1}^2 x^{p+q -2(n+m+1)} \mathrm{d} x
   X_{pq} = \sum_{n=0}^{\lfloor \frac{p-1}{2} \rfloor} \sum_{m=0}^{\lfloor \frac{q-1}{2} \rfloor} c_{p,n} c_{q,m} \frac{2^{p+q -2(n+m) -1} + (-1)^{p+q}}{p+q -2(n+m) -1} 
